Position Determination Service API GPS Capability Codes. More...

Detailed Description

GPS capability (Value - Capability)

  • 0 - None
  • 1 - Standalone
  • 2 - Assisted (including XTRA and implying standalone is also supported)
  • 3 - Assisted (without XTRA and implying standalone is also supported)
  • 0xFFFFFFFF - Unknown
